org.eclipse.viatra.emf.mwe2integration

Interface IMessageProcessor<ParameterType,Message extends IMessage<ParameterType>>

  • Type Parameters:
    ParameterType -
    Message -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringMessageProcessor

    public interface IMessageProcessor<ParameterType,Message extends IMessage<ParameterType>>
    Interface that defines the base functions of a message processor. The message processors are responsible for processing certain typed messages. The type of these events is specified in the template parameter, while the parameter type of these messages is specified in the template parameter.
    Author:
    Peter Lunk
